room_title: Escape room "Captain's Curse" by Tri-State Escape in Huntington
review: We went to the pirate room, and it was so neat! They really outdid themselves on the ambiance. The clues were fun and challenging and fit in well with the theme. I cannot wait to try another room!

room_title: Escape room "Captain's Curse" by Tri-State Escape in Huntington
review: We had a great time in the Pirate escape room. We will be going back, the family wants to try the jailbreak room next time. I would recommend this place for a family, friends, or work group outing!
